name: .FUI File Extension
summary: Learn about .FUI files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: You can open FUI files with Minecraft FUI Editor (Windows), FUI Studio (Windows), and PhoenixARC Calcite Editor (Windows). These programs allow you to edit or replace the images the FUI file contains.
